             java.lang.String notes)
        Constructor for a order object
        Parameters:
        order_id - the id of the order
        primary_distributor_key - primary key used by the distributor
        secondary_key - any other signifiers or keys connected to the order
        distributor - the distributor sending out the order
        store_front - the store front requesting the order
        rate - the rate object associated with the distributor AND store front
        cubes - the cubic feet amount for the order
        weight - the weight of the order
        pieces - the number of pieces the order is comprised of
        merch_price - the price of the merchandise that comprises the order
        notes - the notes associated with the order
